gomodel:SYNGO_1463  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099061 replaced by GO:0098839" , "Rationale: Localisation of NMDR subunits with immunogold EM\n\n8/9/2017 Pim\n- Fig.4 show pre and postsynaptic localization in mossy fiber synapses.\n- Based on the known transmembrane topology of the protein, the \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was chosen.. Experimental description: For postembedding immunogold cytochemistry, three adult male Wistar rats (150-250g, Scanbur, Sollentuna, Sweden) were deeply anesthetized with pentobarbital and fixed by transcardiac perfusion, with a mixture of 0.1% glutaraldehyde and 4% paraformaldehyde in phosphate buffer (pH 7.4; 50 mL/ min for 20 min), after a brief flush of 5% dextran (MW 70,000) in the same buffer." ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-9425-2935" ;
        dc:date           "2024-03-14" ;
        dc:title          "SYNGO_CC_1463" ;
        pav:providedBy    "https://syngo.vu.nl" ;
        biolink:in_taxon  "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/NCBITaxon_10116" .

